title: Ingmar Bergman - Ansiktet / The Face / The Magician - 1958
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0051365/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0051365/</a>

A nearly silent appearance by Max von Sydow, and with an Emperor Ming beard to boot!

The story covers a group of society men placing wagers on the existence of the paranormal, and a group of circus charlatans as their victims.  A lovely, if a bit slutty, performance by Bibi Andersson.  And a cross-dressing Ingrid Thulin...

Try to avoid the Criterion "Seventh Seal" extras before viewing this, as it presents most of the last 15 minutes of the film - what a silly idea.
